ccessible angle/location next to the bed) \nand the patient does not require helper assistance during toilet transfers. \n\n\u2022  Code 05, Setup or clean-up assistance, if the only help a patient needs to complete the toilet transfer activity \n\nis for a helper to retrieve and place the toilet seat riser and remove it after patient use.", "type": "Document"}}